Q. How to instantiate chrome driver?
=>  System.setProperty("webdriver.chrome.driver", "Chrome Driver executable location on your system"); 
    WebDriver driver = new ChromeDriver(); //=>instantiate a Chrome browser in safe mode, with no plugins and extensions.
    
Q. How to instantiate firefox driver?
=>  System.setProperty("webdriver.gecko.driver", "Gecko Driver executable location on your system"); 
    WebDriver driver = new FirefoxDriver();
    
Q. What is desired capabilities?
=>  Desired Capabilities help Selenium understand the browser details, like its name, version, and OS.

Q. What are the Browser Commands?
=> driver.get(URL)
   String title = driver.getTitle()
   String pageSource = driver.getPageSource()
   String currentURL = driver.getCurrentUrl()
   driver.close()
   driver.quit()

Q. How to Open a WebPage in Selenium?
=> driver.get(appUrl): Load a new web page in the current browser window.

